@startuml
skinparam monochrome true

scale 10 as 150 pixels

robust "simulationTimer" as Timer
concise "GalaxyPhysicsController" as Physics
concise "GraphWidget" as UI

@0
Timer is Idle
Physics is Idle
UI is Idle

@16
Timer is Tick
Timer -> Physics : onPhysicsTimerTick()
Physics is Simulating

@18
Timer is Idle

@26
Physics is Idle
note bottom of Physics : Physics step complete\n(Gravity & Springs applied)
Physics -> UI : updateGraphDisplay()
UI is Updating

@30
UI is Idle

@32
Timer is Tick
note top of Timer : Simulation loop repeats\nevery 16ms (approx 60 FPS)
Timer -> Physics : onPhysicsTimerTick()
Physics is Simulating

@34
Timer is Idle

@42
Physics is Idle
Physics -> UI : updateGraphDisplay()
UI is Updating

@46
UI is Idle
@enduml